name: cube runner (itch) (vikky make games)
description: There are a total of 8 levels. The first four levels are basic and for beginners. The next four levels are challenging. The final level is really crazy. There are jumpers, kickers, teleporters. The crazy thing is you can even wall run. The aim of the game is to finish the final level. If this game receives a positive response I will add more updates. Hope you will like the game.
